text:
Yoo stud londe, 
man toh kar rha do char paarivarik sabd yahan likh du, but mahool ko pavitra rakhunga mai.  Saale aadhaar card ki shakal se ladki milte hi hritik roshan ban gya. Tere sath itna spend kiya hai ki meri bandi bhi taane marti hai ab *no homo*. Mai jab bhi koi journey shuru karta hu, toh aksar jo shuru shuru mai dost bante hai, baad mai dost nhi rehte. Tum pehle exception nikle, happily, and ab ye journey life time chalega. Pehli baar best friend ka feel aya kisi se. Akhilesh sarkar ke diye laptop ki izzat rakhli tune, padhai bhi kar liya, launda naach bhi macha diya, juniors ke bich role model bhi ban nikle, and pura umeed hai placement bhi tagda lagega. Movie nights se canteen nights se exam nights se fest nights tak apne memories itne hai ki yahan likhne pe 90% miss hi ho jaenge, ab 5 saal baad coffee house mai baith ke discuss krenge (jiska bill tu pay karega) toh 4-5 ghante yu hi nikal jaenge. Abhi toh humara ek saal sath mai aur bacha hua hai, jisme maine bahut si aur memories banane ka plan bana rakha hai. Ye corona jae, toh bakchodi macha denge! But bhai kasam se, college mai best chiz jo apne sath le jana chahunga, woh hai humari friendship.
Love you bhai <3
All the best!
author: Aditya  Singh

text:
Suyash bhai!
Ultra pro max chaapu
Honda ke daamaad, Bajaj ka bhatija- Kitne saare competiton and scholarships jo tumhe mile, wahi apne aap mai tumhare credibility define karte hai. Tumne woh sab kr liya jo mai nhi kar pane pe regrets karta. Tumhara actively club, padhai and research manage kr pana apne aap mai inspiration hai. Your nature is soo helpful ki first year juniors se lekar senior tak sab tumhe apna go to guy maante hai. Humari sath ki journeys bhi kaafi saari rahi hai. Honda yes, Delhi hour, pura 2 saal  paper pe kaam karna (uspe 2 citations bhi aa gye :P), kanpur mai dinner out..kaafi kuch kiye hai sath mai! Tumhara eye for detail bhi next level hai, Law sir bhi impressed the bhai tumse! Kash ye lockdown nhi hota, toh aur bhi jyada time spend karte, aur memories banate! and tumne apna first Whiskey shot finish bhi kar diya tha (impressive feat!), maine toh aadha pi ke side mai kar diya tha :P (batana mat XD). Tere liye life mai special jagah hai, hope tha kahi sath mai trip kare! Ab future mai milenge and karenge! All the best for your bright future ahead bro! Sath mai touch mai rahenge forever!
